PC Number Date Chapter Bill Dept
 2018-06832018-06-01,  GAC,  ,  , 
ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectExportation Development Canada - Trans Mountain Pipeline Expansion
PrecisOrder Directing Export Development Canada to (1) perform any activity consistent with any authorization obtained from the Minister of International Trade pursuant to section 23 of the Export Development Act in respect of the project known as the TRANS MOUNTAIN PIPELINE EXPANSION; and, (2) do all such ancillary or other things as may be advisable or required to give effect to the provisions contained herein.
